  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/aba7e40de68be2bdbf079d36efdedf06.avif?t=1761218848\" width=800 height=525 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/d726301ae478b4c483e5895ff2220ba0.avif?t=1761218848\" width=614 height=255 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Oasis</h2>In a world without sun, havens of life like the Oasis has developed around sources of lights. These regions are cut off each from other by wastelands of darkness called Abysses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/f6316c7e2dac7e30f4d300b11dc2490f.poster.avif?t=1761218848\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/f6316c7e2dac7e30f4d300b11dc2490f.webm?t=1761218848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/f6316c7e2dac7e30f4d300b11dc2490f.mp4?t=1761218848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Combat</h2>Combine different weapon types and use your equipment skills to create your playstyle! Attacks, spells and combos are the recipe for dynamic combat that tests your dexterity and imagination! Think about it as a group to take on the toughest challenges!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/64ef260861d139ef9528df73727b623b.poster.avif?t=1761218848\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/64ef260861d139ef9528df73727b623b.webm?t=1761218848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/64ef260861d139ef9528df73727b623b.mp4?t=1761218848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Varieties of choice</h2>Unlock a multitude of heroes to try to save the Oasis. Increase their destinies and unlock new ones, as well as numerous equipment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/9f9edf4c41b56ad9b534b0247e01d07d.poster.avif?t=1761218848\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/9f9edf4c41b56ad9b534b0247e01d07d.webm?t=1761218848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/9f9edf4c41b56ad9b534b0247e01d07d.mp4?t=1761218848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Different missions</h2>Adventures taking place in the past will allow you to modify the context of your main quest and achieve your objective... if the temporal balance is not broken.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Versus</h2>Settle your conflicts in a versus mode with the possibility of fighting in 2v2! Upgrade your equipment between each fight and adopt the right strategy to win your revenge!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/d726301ae478b4c483e5895ff2220ba0.avif?t=1761218848\" width=614 height=255 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Oasis</h2>In a world without sun, havens of life like the Oasis has developed around sources of lights. These regions are cut off each from other by wastelands of darkness called Abysses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/f6316c7e2dac7e30f4d300b11dc2490f.poster.avif?t=1761218848\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/f6316c7e2dac7e30f4d300b11dc2490f.webm?t=1761218848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/f6316c7e2dac7e30f4d300b11dc2490f.mp4?t=1761218848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Combat</h2>Combine different weapon types and use your equipment skills to create your playstyle! Attacks, spells and combos are the recipe for dynamic combat that tests your dexterity and imagination! Think about it as a group to take on the toughest challenges!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/64ef260861d139ef9528df73727b623b.poster.avif?t=1761218848\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/64ef260861d139ef9528df73727b623b.webm?t=1761218848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/64ef260861d139ef9528df73727b623b.mp4?t=1761218848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Varieties of choice</h2>Unlock a multitude of heroes to try to save the Oasis. Increase their destinies and unlock new ones, as well as numerous equipment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/9f9edf4c41b56ad9b534b0247e01d07d.poster.avif?t=1761218848\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/9f9edf4c41b56ad9b534b0247e01d07d.webm?t=1761218848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/9f9edf4c41b56ad9b534b0247e01d07d.mp4?t=1761218848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Different missions</h2>Adventures taking place in the past will allow you to modify the context of your main quest and achieve your objective... if the temporal balance is not broken.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Versus</h2>Settle your conflicts in a versus mode with the possibility of fighting in 2v2! Upgrade your equipment between each fight and adopt the right strategy to win your revenge!",
